<h2>Offene Gedichte (Dissertation)</h2>
<h3>Eine Studie über Paul Celans &quot;Die Niemandsrose&quot;</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='385'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
